Relations)) visa in the Pacific Australia Labour Mobility stream;
(ba)
the Subclass 407 (Training) visa;
(bb)
the Subclass 408 (Temporary Activity) visa;
(c)
the Subclass 416 (Special Program) visa;
(e)
the Subclass 420 (Entertainment) visa;
(k)
